{"tid":1624412,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"勇武中場休息，和理文宣全面進場，國際先係主戰場!!","createTime":"2019-10-05T03:48:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-05T04:26:32.000Z","uid":191487,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"ab7e465af28c59cd64dfcde5ffcc118ad529f900","tid":1624412,"uid":191487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:48:32.000Z","msg":"明知推蒙面法並不會有助解決問題，咁做乜要推禁蒙面法？<br />\n<br />\n咪就係要製造紛爭，製造怒氣，製造暴民形象。特別係區選前，美國過香港民主法案前，政府更加需要呢啲確實證據去游說美國。<br />\n<br />\n肉酸既畫面留俾對方做，唔係自己做。特別係對方開槍犯錯禁蒙面，之後就更要和理，將焦點定格係對手身上，而唔係更激烈地搶fo。<br />\n<br />\n玩路軌，大裝修，真係要適可而止。<br />\n勇武既兄弟中場抖抖先，其餘兄弟將精力拎去做文宣，重新聚焦五大訴求。<br />\n<br />\n西方好多都係左膠大國，香港要求國際援助就只可以就住佢地口味。<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命。"},{"pid":"37e964d82335e2d370ba4b065ca4b17c0e382c1b","tid":1624412,"uid":191487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:50:32.000Z","msg":"自推10連"},{"pid":"4397466aeca5fdde8645933c3afaa68de5f89488","tid":1624412,"uid":265555,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:51:22.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c91689fee2bd4a4c86e0ad9628122ae32b58854f","tid":1624412,"uid":191487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:52:48.000Z","msg":"自推2/10"},{"pid":"20aa20a94f29e84fc5e06e38161f9bbb9348b9e5","tid":1624412,"uid":191487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T03:56:06.000Z","msg":"自推3/10"},{"pid":"99d13c1e15dcba78126ce19aacba48db514d6141","tid":1624412,"uid":191487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:00:53.000Z","msg":"自推4/10"},{"pid":"cd43b5023dcb2a75f576f4fc5590ce0041faf773","tid":1624412,"uid":329856,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:03:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c567b0cdb56e14927d3fa6ea18bd6b2ba6751da3","tid":1624412,"uid":191487,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-05T04:09:36.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"3ef5180345ba6504ef68fac5b73b0b8fde5d1bf2","tid":1624412,"uid":257293,"like":0,"di